    <div id="top-featured-message"><h3>Is Your Cryptography Reliable?</h3>
<p>
    Our team specializes in studying real world cryptography implementations
    to assure their correctness and security.
</p>
<p class="top-buttons">
    <a
        class="btn btn-success"
        href="https://paragonie.com/blog/2017/06/why-you-want-paragon-initiative-enterprises-audit-your-code"
    >
        Why You Want to Hire Our Company
    </a>
    <a
        class="btn btn-primary"
        href="https://paragonie.com/contact"
    >
        Contact Us
    </a>
</p>
</div>
    <div class="row">
